                .type-of-room__features-item-img-wrapper
                  img(src="img/bathroom.jpg")
                | раздельный санузел
              li.type-of-room__features-item
                .type-of-cottage__features-item-img-wrapper
                  img(src="img/wi-fi.jpg")
                | WI-FI
      section.type-of-cottage
